My feeling about lpg conversions is........we sort of tried it in the 70's and
80's and it really wasn't worth the trouble.  

I'm much more excited about the possibilities of electric conversions:

http://www.evalbum.com/

You can click on "search" and then "type/make" and then "volkswagen" to see all
the beetles and busses that have been converted.  Ben Graves 1966 microbus is
still my favourite.  Advanced DC's FB1-4001A seems to be the motor of choice,
weighing in at a hefty 150 lb.

Adrian

